Package: CoPro
Title: Detecting Co-Progression Between Cell Types in Spatial Transcriptomics Data
Version: 0.6.1
Maintainer: Zhen Miao <zhenmiao@sas.upenn.edu>
Authors@R: 
    person("Zhen", "Miao", , "zhenmiao@sas.upenn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-3255-9517"))
Description: Detecting co-progression between cell types in spatial 
 transcriptomics data. The method works in both supervised and unsupervised manner,
 so it can be used for explorative data analyses. 
